data.description: Imagine yourself living in the peaceful countryside on 11 breathtaking acres that is ag exempt. Even better, imagine a home that not only has a zero dollar electric bill every month, but the electric company gives you a credit back each month.  The home has solar pannels ran off a battery. This gorgeous home is 2500 square feet with 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, one being a Jack and Jill bathroom, and a extra living room. This home is the perfect set up for entertaining with the oversize covered porch or enjoying your morning coffee while watching the deer roam. The kitchen is a must see with an abundant amount of cabinets, a large oversized fridge, and a walk in pantry. The property has a heavy duty arch entrance with a solar powered gate opener and is fully fenced ready for your horses to call home. The HVAC system was replaced in March of 2022 and in July of 2023 a new water line ran across the entire property. As if all this isn't enough, it's even equipped with a covered RV car port with electric and water connections along with a separate RV septic system. The seller is offering a $4,000 carpet allowance.
